Penne Unna Vida Maten
Nee Enna Maranthaalum

En Manasula Neethan Ninaivu Irupa


Oru Naal Nee Ennai Sandhithaal
Adi Penne Neeyum Sindhippaai
Ennai Yeno Pirindhu Sendru
Un Vaazhvai Neeye Dhandithaai

